@devops-engineer Please review this analysis. If you agree this is a false positive:
1. **Approve the `devops-approval` environment** in the workflow run 2. Go to the Actions tab → Find the running workflow 3. Click "Review deployments" and approve the `devops-approval` environment 4. The workflow will automatically update Concert API to mark this CVE as false positive 5. The issue will be closed automatically after Concert is updated
**What happens after approval:** - Concert API will be updated: Status = "False positive" - Issue will be labeled: `concert-updated`, `false-positive-confirmed` - Issue will be closed automatically
